Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.33,0:02:19.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自由骑士…另一个新的传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.31,0:02:25.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在阿烈克拉岛南方有个罗德岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.18,0:02:30.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因大地之神玛发和邪神卡底斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.25,0:02:33.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所产生的这个岛屿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.59,0:02:35.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都在讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.69,0:02:37.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个被诅咒的岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.36,0:02:44.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在刚结束战争的罗德岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.70,0:02:47.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又有人开始有新的野心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到会有麻莫的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.31,0:02:56.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来这大地之神玛发的神殿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什么事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那剑上的是什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.65,0:03:06.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那把剑背负著人类所有的哀怨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.22,0:03:09.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来是魔王所拥有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.42,0:03:14.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它应该是被封印住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.40,0:03:19.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，我不是来听你讲这些的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.70,0:03:22.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来是有事想问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.24,0:03:25.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能讲实话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.41,0:03:28.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会说谎的，但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.88,0:03:31.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧，只要把你能知道的事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.78,0:03:33.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都讲出来就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.21,0:03:36.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火龙所拥有的宝物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宝物！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.39,0:03:43.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想将那宝藏占为已有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.06,0:03:46.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古代的魔王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.69,0:03:51.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将一些宝物分别让五条龙看守著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.17,0:03:56.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是其中的冰龙却没有宝藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.30,0:03:59.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看过冰龙了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.37,0:04:02.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受到那家伙非常不友好的欢迎仪式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.28,0:04:07.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但它现在应该很後悔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.65,0:04:13.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它现在应该是在冬眠中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.89,0:04:18.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你却攻击它，把它杀死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.29,0:04:23.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说有人帮它把诅咒给解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你是其中的一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它又把宝藏全部给了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.70,0:04:29.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那些宝藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.57,0:04:33.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都用在修理这神殿上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.84,0:04:40.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要找的不是用钱能买到的宝藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.01,0:04:43.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我没来找过你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.95,0:04:44.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.35,0:04:49.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉，是想统一这岛的麻莫王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.86,0:04:52.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.39,0:04:56.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那恕我多问一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.26,0:05:01.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么想要得到魔王的秘宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.74,0:05:04.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了要完成死去的国王的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.94,0:05:06.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我最应该完成的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.91,0:05:08.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一定要拿到秘宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.94,0:05:11.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔王的秘宝，支配的王锡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时代又开始要重复了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.36,0:05:27.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前的时代开始远离我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.20,0:05:31.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丽斯大人，那个人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.23,0:05:34.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，你可不可以把斯林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.07,0:05:38.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和谢西努还有小孙女叫回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.41,0:05:41.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个罗德岛的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.38,0:05:44.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就交给他们这些小孩子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.59,0:05:57.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森，你走得太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.56,0:05:59.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人是不会逃走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.56,0:06:02.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我希望他们逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不想看到无辜的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.97,0:06:06.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这士兵真是特别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.03,0:06:10.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然连到一个村庄打仗都怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.94,0:06:15.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森，你要弄清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.08,0:06:18.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是去收他们未缴的税而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.08,0:06:22.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是不想把这里弄成像战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.12,0:06:25.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然也是要对方能够乖乖听话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.35,0:06:28.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他们听话也是工作之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.39,0:06:32.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听著，波里森他给我们的酬劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.79,0:06:35.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是收回来的钱的四分之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.26,0:06:38.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里可以找到这么好赚的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你也要用心一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.60,0:06:45.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这样讲你都没有反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不想做的话可以退出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种胆小的佣兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.14,0:06:53.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点消失比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.75,0:06:57.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先声明，最好别让我同伴生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.35,0:06:59.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果让他生气起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.19,0:07:02.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是敌人是朋友他都不会分的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.56,0:07:09.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.90,0:07:12.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请大家照计划去进行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢西努先生，谢西努先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，迪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.68,0:07:30.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢斯那家伙找人来要钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.52,0:07:32.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我们把代表叫出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.52,0:07:34.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找贤者斯林吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.46,0:07:37.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，他们讲因为国王的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.12,0:07:39.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我们交税
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.33,0:07:42.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？就让我去把他们赶走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.23,0:07:43.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.23,0:07:48.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以防万一，你去帮我叫他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.04,0:07:51.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.21,0:07:55.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们居然让国王的使者在这里等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要利用那些东西当武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.51,0:08:03.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村子里有个魔法师就那么神气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.32,0:08:06.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才一个魔法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.65,0:08:07.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.02,0:08:09.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢西努先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.39,0:08:11.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是村子的代表吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.19,0:08:14.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，我跟你讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.43,0:08:18.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们和你们国家一点关系都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.00,0:08:20.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是自耕自足的村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.13,0:08:24.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以没必要交给你们税
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.34,0:08:28.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白的话就快点离开这村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.11,0:08:34.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你向这村子施了什么魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.65,0:08:36.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他们这样听话，假魔法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.58,0:08:38.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么，你敢污辱我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.45,0:08:48.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…… ……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.46,0:08:50.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森，大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.93,0:08:53.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了，退後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.87,0:08:58.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万能的火请变成破坏之火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.81,0:08:59.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要再退一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.17,0:09:02.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烧不到这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.48,0:09:12.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烧到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.75,0:09:14.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个会使用火的魔法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.46,0:09:17.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要不被火打中就没有关系了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.76,0:09:19.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.49,0:09:22.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.23,0:09:25.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他真的是个魔法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人告诉我，我们快逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.57,0:09:30.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你们逃走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.11,0:09:34.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.61,0:09:37.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好!是圈套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.61,0:09:42.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是，想不到你的头脑那么简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.05,0:09:47.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个样子你就不能一次全解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.39,0:09:53.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你把那贤者丈给丢掉，斯林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.39,0:09:55.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.30,0:09:59.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样，这村子的自卫团长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.43,0:10:03.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫谢西努，是斯林的弟子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.90,0:10:05.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然有二个魔法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.51,0:10:08.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢斯讲过只有一个魔法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.51,0:10:10.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.44,0:10:13.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我们已经抓到一个人质了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.65,0:10:17.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想利用我做人质去逼他们缴税
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.25,0:10:20.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没那么容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.55,0:10:21.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要杀就杀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.42,0:10:24.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真勇敢，就成全你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.33,0:10:26.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的有必要杀他吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.49,0:10:28.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.26,0:10:31.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果生意做不成，我们就完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.10,0:10:37.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想後悔的话就趁现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你施了保护的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事了，谢西努
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.28,0:10:52.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.05,0:10:54.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.32,0:10:59.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!风的精灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.93,0:11:01.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是魔法师吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.00,0:11:04.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是他做的，是贺而夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.23,0:11:06.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贺而夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.37,0:11:16.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢西努真是的，每次都这么冒失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.88,0:11:17.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒂都小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.51,0:11:20.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢西努，剩下来就交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.18,0:11:23.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们别再闹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.79,0:11:28.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然我不会原谅你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母，我听过他的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.59,0:11:33.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带著贺而夫的剑客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.13,0:11:36.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是传说中的自由骑士帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.93,0:11:38.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己一个人会有危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.97,0:11:40.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准插手，波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.93,0:11:43.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，我早就想和你较量一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.00,0:11:47.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去帮我挡住那二个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.44,0:11:48.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让他们施魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.53,0:12:12.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡眠之灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自由的贺而夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.14,0:12:20.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去帮忙把时间停止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.12,0:12:30.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒂都小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.15,0:12:35.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万能的火焰，请变成破坏之火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.76,0:12:41.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底对他做了什么事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.89,0:12:43.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对他施了魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.63,0:12:45.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想让他暂时停下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.97,0:12:50.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是好像对他一点作用都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.48,0:12:59.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放下剑吧，你是赢不了我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.51,0:13:01.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.52,0:13:09.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往这边来了，蒂都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.96,0:13:11.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.16,0:13:47.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你赢了，剑客先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.03,0:13:50.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想听你的解释
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.20,0:13:54.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然，我输了就一定会服从你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.71,0:14:02.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不可以杀我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.78,0:14:05.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就会听你的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.91,0:14:08.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.66,0:14:24.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快把剑放下，波里森他……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.67,0:14:26.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃!帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.67,0:14:28.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.59,0:14:47.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手，波里森，我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.26,0:14:52.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森你不认识我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.46,0:14:54.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难不得我觉得很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么法术对他都没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.43,0:14:59.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人是狂战土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.50,0:15:00.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狂战士?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.17,0:15:04.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人被愤怒精灵尤利控制著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.24,0:15:08.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的心里只有破坏和杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.41,0:15:10.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讲什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.91,0:15:12.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变成狂战士的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.81,0:15:14.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他分辨不出对方是敌是友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.08,0:15:17.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会一直杀到对方变成血肉模糊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.82,0:15:20.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑，前面就是村子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.22,0:15:22.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被他进去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.09,0:15:23.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.06,0:15:33.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森，住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.13,0:15:36.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手，波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.01,0:15:44.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.81,0:15:49.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.55,0:15:55.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此，这就是狂战土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.46,0:15:57.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.59,0:15:59.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在发什么呆，趁这时候快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁讲过要你来救我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.93,0:16:09.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有那么大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.89,0:16:29.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒂都，这家伙用剑是打不赢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.76,0:16:30.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.13,0:16:37.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温柔的森林精灵请赐我力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.24,0:16:43.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗的精灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.87,0:16:46.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌握恐怖的精灵谢幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.54,0:16:50.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请帮忙平息那男人的愤怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.42,0:17:01.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有效了，做得好，蒂都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.02,0:17:05.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔力精灵，黑暗精灵，困难精灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.99,0:17:07.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森，听得见我的声音吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.23,0:17:09.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点清醒过来，波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母，已经停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.40,0:17:19.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.71,0:17:21.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，别杀他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.71,0:17:22.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.24,0:17:26.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我不允许，他已经不是狂战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.01,0:17:28.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他变回平常人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.85,0:17:29.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.02,0:17:32.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不让，我不能看我朋友被杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.22,0:17:41.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友…帮他包扎伤口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到村子里去讲个清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森，波里森，振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.67,0:17:58.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森以前亲眼看到姐姐被杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.38,0:18:02.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他只要看到有女人被欺负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.92,0:18:04.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会变成那个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.92,0:18:07.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再讲也没有用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有那场战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.59,0:18:14.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森也许也不会变成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.23,0:18:18.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然英雄战争已经结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.03,0:18:22.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是後遗症还留在这岛上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.07,0:18:25.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们想怎样处置我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.34,0:18:28.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你可以发誓不再来这村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.64,0:18:30.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就放你走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.78,0:18:32.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带著那个危险的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.75,0:18:36.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好热闹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.62,0:18:37.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯林贤者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.58,0:18:39.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你们回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.29,0:18:42.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母，你好像很累的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.16,0:18:48.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然，为了保护村子，差点没命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.20,0:18:50.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然是会累的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.63,0:18:55.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很少见你和蕾里小丽斯一起出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.27,0:18:58.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小丽斯，你们到哪里去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.81,0:19:03.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到北方的玛发神殿去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.51,0:19:05.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛发神殿的丽斯那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.25,0:19:11.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样，母亲拜托我一件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.72,0:19:12.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的事，想请帕母也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.02,0:19:13.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.49,0:19:18.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天就行了，连龙都帮你杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.43,0:19:21.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗，这样就太感谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.33,0:19:24.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我本来就不知道该怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.10,0:19:27.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你去帮我对付龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.97,0:19:29.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来问题就解决了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.70,0:19:32.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要和龙打？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.44,0:19:36.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对!为了罗德岛，必须这样
